OL,5,GThe 50th birthday of Emmerdale this
OL,6,Gmonth also marks the golden anniversary
OL,7,Gof regular afternoon television.
OL,9,FIt seems incredible to think that the
OL,10,Fidea of afternoon entertainment was
OL,11,Fonce considered controversial.
OL,13,FUntil 1972 television broadcasting
OL,14,Fhours were limited by law.
OL,16,FThe rule was designed to protect the
OL,17,FBBC  the argument was that any
OL,18,Fextension to ITV's hours would need to
OL,19,Fbe matched by BBC One so would either
OL,20,Fmean resources being stretched or a
OL,21,Fhigher licence fee.
OL,3,C50th anniversary of regular afternoon
OL,4,CTV
OL,22,                                   G1/8
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
