OL,5,FThe IBA (as it had just become) ensured
OL,6,Fthe extension to ITV's hours provided a
OL,7,Fproper balance of viewing. The
OL,8,Fintroduction of weekday afternoon
OL,9,Fviewing was the most significant
OL,10,Fdevelopment.
OL,12,FBut as well as soaps like Emmerdale
OL,13,FFarm and General Hospital there was
OL,14,Fmuch more.
OL,16,FA lunchtime news bulletin, pre-school
OL,17,Fprogrammes, programmes from the smaller
OL,18,Fregions with little access to the
OL,19,Fnetwork, repeats of prestigious evening
OL,20,Fprogrammes, magazine features.
OL,3,C50th anniversary of regular afternoon
OL,4,CTV
OL,22,                                   G3/8
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G
