PN,35204
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1667777620
OL,5,FIt seems incredible it took so long.
OL,7,FThe BBC had some afternoon programmes
OL,8,Fin the 50s and early 60s, often
OL,9,Fexplicitly aimed at women. Many ITV
OL,10,Fregions had cheap but popular lunchtime
OL,11,Fvariety shows in their early days.
OL,13,FNobody could pretend a market for
OL,14,Fafternoon TV did not exist.
OL,16,FInterestingly when the restrictions
OL,17,Fwere lifted (with little meaningful
OL,18,Fcriticism) some papers spoke of "all
OL,19,Fday" television. Of course, this took
OL,20,Fanother decade-and-a-half.
OL,3,C50th anniversary of regular afternoon
OL,4,CTV
