OL,5,FThe weekend schedule also benefited 
OL,6,Fthe relaxation allowed LWT to launch
OL,7,Fthe Sunday current affairs programme
OL,8,FWeekend World.
OL,10,FITV never looked back but the BBC's
OL,11,Fattitude to weekday afternoon TV for
OL,12,Fmany years was a sad reflection on the
OL,13,Fcorporation's financial state.
OL,15,FIt was not for want of effort or
OL,16,Fconcern by individuals.
OL,3,C50th anniversary of regular afternoon
OL,4,CTV
