OL,5,FIt took until 1983 for the BBC to
OL,6,Fregularly start offering afternoon
OL,7,Fentertainment only for history to
OL,8,Frepeat itself soon afterwards.
OL,10,FWhen the BBC finally launched an
OL,11,Fofficial daytime service in 1986, it
OL,12,Fwould have been hard not to wonder if
OL,13,Fit was really there to stay as
OL,14,Fpromised.
OL,16,FToday 24-hour TV is taken for granted.
OL,17,FBut the impact of the 1972 extension to
OL,18,Fhours should not be overlooked. It was
OL,19,Fa milestone in TV history.
OL,3,C50th anniversary of regular afternoon
