OL,5,FIt brought a lot of pleasure to people
OL,6,Fat home during the day  especially the
OL,7,Fold, the housebound and shiftworkers.
OL,8,FPeople who could often be overlooked
OL,9,Fand who should not be classed alongside
OL,10,Fsquare-eyed couch potatoes.
